information: The company AMMERLÄNDER SCHINKENDIELE INH. UWE GUNDLACH E.K., is a Wholesaler, founded in 1974, which operates in the Eggs industry. It also operates in the Meat, Offal, Dairy products, and Meats, cooked and cured industries. It is based in Bad Zwischenahn, Germany.
